Medvedev Fires Head of Russian Radio-Electronic Warfare Troops

-- B y   L y u b o v   P r o n i n a
-- 
2011-07-15T05:35:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-15/medvedev-fires-head-of-russian-radio-electronic-warfare-troops.html
President  Dmitry Medvedev  fired the
head of the Russian army’s radio-electronic warfare troops,
General Oleg Ivanov, the Kremlin said.  Medvedev also fired the military’s personnel chief, General
Sergei Chvarkov, the presidential administration said in an e-
mailed statement today, without giving a reason for either
dismissal.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lyubov Pronina in Moscow at 
 lpronina@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Brad Cook at 
 bcook7@bloomberg.net  